{"tid":2448775,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7.21 CCTV片揭黑衫男失知覺仍遭棍打 「9白衣人圍毆」證人需駁骨","createTime":"2021-03-16T07:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T07:20:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5b328d1c90ef1140329ab046a2d8baccd9c003c6","tid":2448775,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T07:20:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210316/CCGOKP7HDJEU5OIDPGZZQSJRJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210316%2FCCGOKP7HDJEU5OIDPGZZQSJRJU%2F&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirDr7MFgrQ0V0XG6LyL0fmAc%3D&h=a3c5155d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210316%2FCCGOKP7HDJEU5OIDPGZZQSJRJU%2F&h=9b3b54c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210316/CCGOKP7HDJEU5OIDPGZZQSJRJU/</a><br />\n<br />\n7.21 CCTV片揭黑衫男失知覺仍遭棍打<br />\n「9白衣人圍毆」證人需駁骨<br />\n <img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Xki4jgyyjBH1CkkDv4Mnw5Hm1MA=/1701x676/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G6VDL4ZMXFERZFKYJNGILCVG2I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXki4jgyyjBH1CkkDv4Mnw5Hm1MA%3D%2F1701x676%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG6VDL4ZMXFERZFKYJNGILCVG2I.jpg&h=7ef15c55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■六名被告昨出庭應訊；另外兩名被告林觀良及林啟明承認暴動罪，還柙候判。<br />\n<br />\n手機用戶請按此放大圖表<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：稱無印象大堂睹白衣人<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】7.21白衣人暴動案昨續審，控方傳召最後一名證人出庭。接獲居民求助的證人O稱，他為阻止施襲的白衣人，被九人圍毆至手肘骨裂，接受兩次駁骨手術、近一年的物理治療，才恢復手臂的正常活動能力。庭上片段顯示，一名持傘黑衫男遭至少14名白衣人不斷圍毆，受襲倒地後疑失去知覺；惟有白衣人似仍未滿足，路過時再用長棍施襲洩憤。<br />\n<br />\n證人O供稱，白衣人當晚經扶手梯衝上J出口，當時J出口已落閘，情況趨緩和，惟其後雙方開始互相擲物和攻擊。O指最初閘外只有三至四人，其後增至「十個八個」，身處大堂的他希望勸阻白衣人，故走近捲閘，但突然有長形物件在閘外「飛入嚟」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做一年物理治療<br />\n<br />\n白衣人群拉起捲閘一刻，O自稱在旁叫謂：「唔好！」他庭上解釋意指「唔好衝入嚟」、「唔好襲擊」，惟當時無人理會。O指白衣人拉閘後衝向K出口方向，部份人攻擊站內人士，但他沒留意白衣人有否叫囂。O目擊一名黑衣。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nO沒提供醫療報告，僅稱右手肘骨裂，身體各處有瘀傷。法官葉佐文追問：「可唔可以仔細少少呀？」O憑記憶。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n控方播放閉路電視片段，顯示白衣人衝入大堂之前。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n餘下被告包括王志榮、黃英傑、「飛天南」吳偉南、鄧英斌，以及蔡立基（介乎40至61歲），聆訊今續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC888/19、DCCC11、DCCC734/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OCfwBgda8bIzXjCCyBVsJhsKoUM=/1523x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5TKN2NYT2JG2DCESQVEXNIMLH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOCfwBgda8bIzXjCCyBVsJhsKoUM%3D%2F1523x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5TKN2NYT2JG2DCESQVEXNIMLH4.jpg&h=da53ba17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■控方片段顯示有黑衫男子遭13名白衣人圍毆。"}]}